  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Security] At the end of the battle, you may play 1 [Diaboromon]
    Token without paying its memory cost. (Diaboromon Tokens are level 6 white Digimon
    with a memory cost of 14, 3000 DP, and Mega/Unknown/Unidentified traits.)[Opponent's
    Turn] All of your [Diaboromon] gain \uFF1CBlocker\uFF1E. (When an opponent's
    Digimon attacks, you may suspend this Digimon to force the opponent to attack
    it instead.)"
